                        <li>Trauma and fracture surgeries</li>
                        <li>Shoulder surgeries</li>
                        <li>Management of arthritis</li>
                        <li>Treatment of osteomyelitis</li>
                        <li>Keyhole surgeries such as arthroscopic ligament reconstruction (ACL), meniscus and chondral surgeries</li>
                        <li>Management of open fractures, limbs lengthening using Ilizarov method</li>
                        <li>Fusion of joints (Arthrodesis)</li>
                        <li>Disc surgery, fusion surgeries for spine instability</li>
                        <li>Surgery for correction of spinal deformities like scoliosis and spondylolisthesis</li>
                        <li>Paediatric orthopedic surgeries for clubfoot, congenital hip dysplasia, bone and joint infection management</li>
                        <li>Management of juvenile arthritis and metabolic bone disorders</li>
